Package: mizerExtensionTemplate
Title: Template for mizer Extension Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A template that demonstrates all extension mechanisms available in
    mizer. Use it as a starting point for your own mizer extension package.
    The template illustrates metadata-only and dispatching extensions, external
    encounter and mortality terms, a custom rate method via S3 dispatch
    (replacing setRateFunction()), a dynamical component via setComponent(),
    and user-facing generic overrides with NextMethod() chaining.
